data.title: Charles A. “Rust Epique” Lopez (1968
data.meta_description: Rock Musician. Rust was the guitarist for the rock band Crazy Town, who had a number 1 pop and rock hit in 2001 with Butterfly. Rust left the group after the success of their Top 10 album Gift of Game and had recently formed 'Prething,' whose debut album is scheduled for release on April 6, and from which the single...
